{"title": [{"text": "Query Understanding in Web Search -by Large Scale Log Data Mining and Statistical Learning", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "Query Understanding", "start_pos": 0, "end_pos": 19, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.7610064744949341}, {"text": "Log Data Mining", "start_pos": 50, "end_pos": 65, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.6470211247603098}, {"text": "Statistical Learning", "start_pos": 70, "end_pos": 90, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8243943452835083}]}], "abstractContent": [{"text": "Query understanding is an important component of web search, like document understanding, query document matching, ranking, and user understanding.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "Query understanding", "start_pos": 0, "end_pos": 19, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8381513953208923}, {"text": "document understanding", "start_pos": 66, "end_pos": 88, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.7777252495288849}, {"text": "query document matching", "start_pos": 90, "end_pos": 113, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.6253363788127899}, {"text": "user understanding", "start_pos": 128, "end_pos": 146, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.7139483392238617}]}, {"text": "The goal of query understanding is to predict the user's search intent from the given query.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "query understanding", "start_pos": 12, "end_pos": 31, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8236470520496368}]}, {"text": "Needless to say, search log mining and statistical learning are fundamental technologies to address the task of query understanding.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "search log mining", "start_pos": 17, "end_pos": 34, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.6632470488548279}, {"text": "statistical learning", "start_pos": 39, "end_pos": 59, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8171315491199493}, {"text": "query understanding", "start_pos": 112, "end_pos": 131, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.7657617628574371}]}, {"text": "In this talk, I will first introduce a large-scale search log mining platform which we have developed at MSRA.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "search log mining", "start_pos": 51, "end_pos": 68, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.6755232016245524}, {"text": "MSRA", "start_pos": 105, "end_pos": 109, "type": "DATASET", "confidence": 0.9507683515548706}]}, {"text": "I will then explain our approach to query understanding, as well as document understanding, query document matching, and user understanding.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "query understanding", "start_pos": 36, "end_pos": 55, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8352125585079193}, {"text": "document understanding", "start_pos": 68, "end_pos": 90, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.7520256042480469}, {"text": "query document matching", "start_pos": 92, "end_pos": 115, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.6293604175249735}, {"text": "user understanding", "start_pos": 121, "end_pos": 139, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.7608118653297424}]}, {"text": "After that, I will describe in details about our methods for query understanding based on statistical learning.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "query understanding", "start_pos": 61, "end_pos": 80, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8059479296207428}]}, {"text": "They include query refinement using CRF, named entity recognition in query using topic model, context aware query topic prediction using HMM.", "labels": [], "entities": [{"text": "query refinement", "start_pos": 13, "end_pos": 29, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.8458449840545654}, {"text": "named entity recognition", "start_pos": 41, "end_pos": 65, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.618826667467753}, {"text": "context aware query topic prediction", "start_pos": 94, "end_pos": 130, "type": "TASK", "confidence": 0.5806621789932251}]}, {"text": "This is joint work with Gu Xu, Daxin Jiang and other collaborators.", "labels": [], "entities": []}], "introductionContent": [], "datasetContent": [], "tableCaptions": []}